Workspace setContents: 'ABCDE'.
Workspace cursor moveToIndex: 5 line: 0 column: 5 topLine: 0.
Workspace selection setStartLine: 0 startColumn: 1 endLine: 0 endColumn: 4.
(KernelInstaller objectNamed: 'BootWorkspaceEditorSurface')
    drawSource: Workspace contents
    status: 'READY'
    feedback: 'OUT> SELECTION'
    onForm: Display defaultForm.
